<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cold-n">cold <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kəʊld/    美 /koʊld/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 冷；寒冷：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I couldn’t move my legs because of the cold.
因为天气很冷，我的脚都冻僵了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He suffered a great deal from cold and hunger.
他饥寒交迫。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 伤风；感冒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>I’ve got</strong> a heavy / bad <strong>cold</strong>. 
我患了重感冒。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you take more physical exercises, you will not <strong>catch a cold</strong> so easily.
多参加些体育锻炼，你就不那么容易感冒了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>coldly /'kəʊldli/ adv <br />
coldness /'kəʊldnəs/ n   </p></div>